    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fine-quality calf or lamb parchment used  for writing, illuminations, or binding books. The terms "vellum" and "parchment" are sometimes confused and used interchangeably.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
